          "script": "\n\tfor b in self.view.custom.Selections:\n\t\t\n\t\tif b[\u0027widgetUUID\u0027] \u003d\u003d payload[\u0027buttonIndex\u0027]:\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\tb[\u0027selected\u0027] \u003d payload[\u0027selected\u0027]\n\t\telif b[\u0027widgetUUID\u0027] !\u003d payload[\u0027buttonIndex\u0027] and self.view.custom.operationDetails.multiSelectable \u003d\u003d False:\n\t\t\tsystem.perspective.sendMessage(\u0027deselected\u0027, payload \u003d {\u0027index\u0027: b[\u0027widgetUUID\u0027]})\n\t\t\tb[\u0027selected\u0027] \u003d 0",
